Global Variable# kCFURLUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey

tvOS 9.0–9.0DeprecatedvisionOS 1.0–1.0DeprecatedwatchOS 2.0–2.0Deprecated

```
let kCFURLUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey: CFString!
```

Deprecated

Use NSMetadataQuery and NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey on NSMetadataItem instead

## [Discussion](/documentation/CoreFoundation/kCFURLUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey#Discussion)

A `CFNumber` value that provides the status of the upload in progress.

Deprecated. Use [`NSMetadataQuery`](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataQuery) and [`NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey`](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey) on [`NSMetadataItem`](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataItem) instead.
